data.title: IRAN Sleeping Giant at A Turning Point
data.meta_description:
IRAN; Sleeping Giant at a Turning Point - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This is a comprehensive report on the Iranian economy as well as stock market in 2013 by Mofid Securities. 
We have tried to make it as brief as possible, so if you are looking for specific information on Iran you may not find in this report. Please contact me for more inquiry: seifollahi@emofid.com 
Also after reading this document please send us your feedback on the above email address.
